        {
          "character": "柳梦梅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀呸！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（簇御林） 全不见些影儿哪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "柳梦梅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓小娘子，小生孤单在此，少不得将小娘子的画像，做个伴侣，早晚么，玩之，\n叫之，拜之，赞、赞、赞之！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（尾声） 俺拾得个人儿先庆贺。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "敢柳和梅有些瓜葛？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "美人吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只被你有影无行盼煞我。"
        },
        {
          "character": "柳梦梅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓小娘子，这里有风，请到里边去。唷，小娘子是客，自然小娘子先请，小生\n么，随后。唵，请吓！请请请吓！阿呀来㖸！哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（柳梦梅下。）"
        }
      ],
